com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.speech_to_text.v1.model

Interface CreateJobOptions.Model

  • Enclosing class:
    CreateJobOptions

    public static interface CreateJobOptions.Model
    The identifier of the model that is to be used for the recognition request. See [Languages and models](https://cloud.ibm.com/docs/services/speech-to-text/models.html).
